 <title>Знаете ли вы свою страну?</title>
 <link>https://www.rgo.ru/ru/article/znaete-li-vy-svoyu-stranu</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-link field-type-link-field field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Источник:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://sovch.chuvashia.com/?p=175133&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Советская Чувашия&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;view view-headimage-node view-id-headimage_node view-display-id-entity_view_1 view-dom-id-d6d68c73c41d7fbd5777f8024b18cc1b&quot;&gt;
      
  
  
  
